  <brief_title>Comfort and Tolerance of Surface Neuro Muscular Electrical Stimulation in Parkinson's Disease.</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Evaluation of Comfort and Tolerance of Surface Neuro Muscular Electrical Stimulation (NMES), When Applied to Parkinson's Disease Patients for Both Sensory and Motor Activation.</official_title>
